Application of Woodrow W. GAINEY, Jr., for Habeas Corpus. No. 14316. United States Court of Appeals Third Circuit. Submitted May 24, 1963. Decided May 31, 1963. Mr. Woodrow W. Gainey, Jr., pro se. Gustave Diamond, U. S. Atty., Pittsburgh, Pa., for appellee.

Before KALODNER, STALEY and SMITH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On review of the record we find no error. The Order of the District Court dated November 2, 1962 will be affirmed.
